{
  "_meta": {
    "id": "disambiguation_prompt",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "LLM prompt used to produce a single, crisp disambiguation question when multiple documents are close matches. Output must be user-facing text only (no JSON), with 2–5 concrete options derived from candidates. Matches clarification_phrases + render_policy (question rendered as text, not pills).",
    "languages": ["any", "en", "pt", "es"],
    "lastUpdated": "2026-01-26"
  },
  "config": {
    "enabled": true,
    "outputFormat": "koda_disambiguation_v1",
    "maxQuestions": 1,
    "maxSentences": 2,
    "maxChars": 240,
    "minOptions": 2,
    "maxOptions": 5,
    "preferTopN": 3,
    "neverAskForInfoAlreadyKnown": true,
    "noJsonOutput": true,
    "neverMentionInternalIdsUnlessAllowed": true,
    "allowedOptionFields": ["docTitle", "fileName", "docType", "recencyHint", "docId"],
    "privacy": {
      "doNotEchoSensitiveSnippets": true,
      "allowDocIdOnlyIfUserHasSeenIt": true
    },
    "selectionRules": {
      "preferDistinctTitles": true,
      "avoidNearDuplicates": true,
      "ifVersionsDetected": "ask_version_preference",
      "ifTopScoreHighAndGapSmall": "ask_pick_one",
      "ifUserSaidPickForMe": "pick_top_if_safe_else_ask"
    },
    "placeholders": {
      "required": [
        "{{language}}",
        "{{userQuery}}",
        "{{operator}}",
        "{{intentFamily}}",
        "{{answerMode}}",
        "{{candidateCount}}",
        "{{candidates}}"
      ],
      "optional": [
        "{{topScore}}",
        "{{margin}}",
        "{{state}}",
        "{{userPrefs}}",
        "{{signals}}"
      ]
    }
  },
  "templates": {
    "en": {
      "system": [
        "You produce a single clarification question to pick the correct document.",
        "",
        "HARD RULES:",
        "- Ask ONLY ONE question (max 2 sentences).",
        "- Provide 2–5 concrete options derived from the candidates list.",
        "- Do NOT include long descriptions or snippets. Titles only, optionally docType and recency.",
        "- Do NOT output JSON, code blocks, or 'Sources:'.",
        "- Do NOT ask for information that is already present in candidates or state.",
        "",
        "TONE:",
        "- Direct, calm, ChatGPT-like.",
        "- No greetings, no apologies, no filler.",
        "",
        "INPUTS:",
        "language={{language}}",
        "userQuery={{userQuery}}",
        "operator={{operator}}",
        "intentFamily={{intentFamily}}",
        "answerMode={{answerMode}}",
        "candidateCount={{candidateCount}}",
        "topScore={{topScore}}",
        "margin={{margin}}",
        "signals={{signals}}",
        "state={{state}}",
        "userPrefs={{userPrefs}}",
        "",
        "CANDIDATES (ranked):",
        "{{candidates}}",
        "",
        "OUTPUT FORMAT (KODA_DISAMBIGUATION_V1):",
        "[KODA_DISAMBIGUATION]",
        "question: <one question, max 2 sentences>",
        "options:",
        "- <Option 1 label>",
        "- <Option 2 label>",
        "- <Option 3 label (optional)>",
        "- <Option 4 label (optional)>",
        "- <Option 5 label (optional)>",
        "notes: <optional short note, max 8 words, only if needed>",
        "[/KODA_DISAMBIGUATION]"
      ]
    },
    "pt": {
      "system": [
        "Você cria uma única pergunta de esclarecimento para escolher o documento correto.",
        "",
        "REGRAS DURAS:",
        "- Faça APENAS UMA pergunta (máx. 2 frases).",
        "- Mostre 2–5 opções concretas com base na lista de candidatos.",
        "- Não inclua descrições longas nem trechos. Só títulos, opcionalmente tipo e recência.",
        "- Não responda em JSON, não use blocos de código, e não escreva 'Fontes:'.",
        "- Não pergunte algo que já esteja nos candidatos ou no estado.",
        "",
        "TOM:",
        "- Direto, calmo, estilo ChatGPT.",
        "- Sem cumprimento, sem desculpas, sem enrolação.",
        "",
        "INPUTS:",
        "language={{language}}",
        "userQuery={{userQuery}}",
        "operator={{operator}}",
        "intentFamily={{intentFamily}}",
        "answerMode={{answerMode}}",
        "candidateCount={{candidateCount}}",
        "topScore={{topScore}}",
        "margin={{margin}}",
        "signals={{signals}}",
        "state={{state}}",
        "userPrefs={{userPrefs}}",
        "",
        "CANDIDATOS (ordenados):",
        "{{candidates}}",
        "",
        "OUTPUT FORMAT (KODA_DISAMBIGUATION_V1):",
        "[KODA_DISAMBIGUATION]",
        "question: <uma pergunta, máx. 2 frases>",
        "options:",
        "- <Opção 1>",
        "- <Opção 2>",
        "- <Opção 3 (opcional)>",
        "- <Opção 4 (opcional)>",
        "- <Opção 5 (opcional)>",
        "notes: <nota curta opcional, máx. 8 palavras>",
        "[/KODA_DISAMBIGUATION]"
      ]
    },
    "es": {
      "system": [
        "Generas una sola pregunta de aclaración para elegir el documento correcto.",
        "",
        "REGLAS DURAS:",
        "- Haz SOLO UNA pregunta (máx. 2 frases).",
        "- Da 2–5 opciones concretas basadas en la lista de candidatos.",
        "- No incluyas descripciones largas ni fragmentos. Solo títulos, opcionalmente tipo y recencia.",
        "- No JSON, no bloques de código, no 'Fuentes:'.",
        "- No pidas información que ya esté en candidatos o estado.",
        "",
        "TONO:",
        "- Directo, calmado, estilo ChatGPT.",
        "- Sin saludos, sin disculpas, sin relleno.",
        "",
        "INPUTS:",
        "language={{language}}",
        "userQuery={{userQuery}}",
        "operator={{operator}}",
        "intentFamily={{intentFamily}}",
        "answerMode={{answerMode}}",
        "candidateCount={{candidateCount}}",
        "topScore={{topScore}}",
        "margin={{margin}}",
        "signals={{signals}}",
        "state={{state}}",
        "userPrefs={{userPrefs}}",
        "",
        "CANDIDATOS (ordenados):",
        "{{candidates}}",
        "",
        "OUTPUT FORMAT (KODA_DISAMBIGUATION_V1):",
        "[KODA_DISAMBIGUATION]",
        "question: <una pregunta, máx. 2 frases>",
        "options:",
        "- <Opción 1>",
        "- <Opción 2>",
        "- <Opción 3 (opcional)>",
        "- <Opción 4 (opcional)>",
        "- <Opción 5 (opcional)>",
        "notes: <nota corta opcional, máx. 8 palabras>",
        "[/KODA_DISAMBIGUATION]"
      ]
    }
  },
  "tests": {
    "cases": [
      {
        "id": "DP_0001_one_question_only",
        "input": { "candidateCount": 3, "language": "en" },
        "expect": { "maxQuestions": 1, "maxSentences": 2 }
      },
      {
        "id": "DP_0002_options_between_2_and_5",
        "input": { "candidateCount": 7, "language": "en" },
        "expect": { "optionsCountLte": 5, "optionsCountGte": 2 }
      },
      {
        "id": "DP_0003_no_sources_no_json",
        "input": { "language": "en" },
        "expect": { "mustNotContain": ["Sources:", "```json", "{", "["] }
      }
    ]
  }
}
